<br>
page 1 = ice DD's.. my biggest and then maybe 2 rings back for kicks, helps if i want to select a small nuke for low lvl mobs.<br>
<br>
page 2 = ice AE's.. anything from rains to pillars... again, just need 2 or 3.  (not that i use em much.. but i like to goof off a lot)<br>
<br>
repeat for fire (okeils included here), lightning, and force spells. (i tossed lev in with lightning cause of similar icon)<br>
<br>
then comes shields best skin, protection, resist ice/fire, resist poison/disease<br>
<br>
then utilities.. like BoF/ASS, root, ultravision, gate, harvest.<br>
<br>
then gates/ports/x-locs<br>
<br>
and all the old spells i just moved past page 30 to get out of the way..<br>
<br>
i'm pretty systematic about it... but then it seems most of us are...<br>
<br>
Goratrix<br>
